@AskCoachKev Losing belly fat comes down to sustained calorie deficit and adherence.
Protein, resistance training, sleep, and daily movement help  but rules like “no food after 7 PM” or exactly 8k steps aren’t physiologically required.
Good framework, just not a guaranteed 90 day formula.

@AskCoachKev Most people think fat loss is cosmetic.

In the clinic we see something different.

Visceral fat drives inflammation, insulin resistance, and years of metabolic damage before anyone realizes it.

@cremieuxrecueil Dear me. The "Obesity Gene".
